<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Marlborough Park</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg"> Given its close proximity to three of the most prominent industrial parks in the city the Meridian, Industrial and Franklin, there are ample employment opportunities for the residents in the community. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">The sprawling green spaces and master-planned walking trails around the neighborhood make it ideal for residential settlement by young couples, growing families, and even retirees.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Marlborough park majorly comprise of detached homes, townhouses and apartment condos that are typically listed at an average price of $315,000.</p>
        </div>
